PN,39901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772136278
OL,3,CSecond man arrested after two men
OL,4,Callegedly enter Mosque 'carrying
OL,5,Cweapons'
OL,7,FA second man has been arrested after a
OL,8,Fman allegedly armed with an axe was
OL,9,Fdetained at a mosque as people
OL,10,Fworshipped during Ramadan.
OL,12,FThe man - who is in his 20s - has been
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of conspiracy to
OL,14,Fcommit a section 18 assault, and
OL,15,Fremains in police custody for
OL,16,Fquestioning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
