PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772136278
OL,3,CSecond man arrested after two men
OL,4,Callegedly enter Mosque 'carrying
OL,5,Cweapons'
OL,7,FPolice were called to Manchester
OL,8,FCentral Mosque, in the Victoria Park
OL,9,Farea in the south of the city, at
OL,10,Faround 8.40pm on 24 February after
OL,11,Freceiving a call about the two men
OL,12,F"acting suspiciously".
OL,14,FA statement from the mosque said
OL,15,Fvolunteers "spotted a suspicious bag"
OL,16,Fbefore approaching and challenging one
OL,17,Fof the men.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772136278
OL,3,CSecond man arrested after two men
OL,4,Callegedly enter Mosque 'carrying
OL,5,Cweapons'
OL,7,FA man in his 50s - who was arrested at
OL,8,Fthe mosque on suspicion of possessing
OL,9,Fan offensive weapon and class B drugs
OL,10,F- remains in custody, with police
OL,11,Fgranted extra time to question him.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,14,Fthey are not looking for anymore
OL,15,Fsuspects, and there is "no
OL,16,Fintelligence to suggest that this
OL,17,Fincident poses a wider threat to the
OL,18,Fcommunity."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772136278
OL,3,CSecond man arrested after two men
OL,4,Callegedly enter Mosque 'carrying
OL,5,Cweapons'
OL,7,FThe force said it has not declared the
OL,8,Fincident as terrorist, but is working
OL,9,Fwith Counter Terrorism Police to
OL,10,Finvestigate.
OL,12,FAssistant Chief Constable John Webster
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our investigation has been
OL,14,Fworking at pace, leading to us making
OL,15,Fan arrest for the outstanding man this
OL,16,Fmorning. Detectives will be conducting
OL,17,Finterviews with him today.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772136278
OL,3,CSecond man arrested after two men
OL,4,Callegedly enter Mosque 'carrying
OL,5,Cweapons'
OL,7,F"We continue to take this incident
OL,8,Fseriously and have been granted extra
OL,9,Ftime by the courts to question the
OL,10,Ffirst man, so we can thoroughly
OL,11,Fexplore all possible lines of enquiry
OL,12,Finto the circumstances.
OL,14,F"We know this has been a concerning
OL,15,Ftime for many of our communities, and
OL,16,Fwe remain committed to acting on any
OL,17,Fconcerns reported to us. You can do
OL,18,Fthis by contacting us on 101 or via
OL,19,Fthe LiveChat function on the GMP
OL,20,Fwebsite.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
