OL,3,CSecond man arrested after two men
OL,4,Callegedly enter Mosque 'carrying
OL,5,Cweapons'
OL,7,F"Alternatively, contact Crimestoppers
OL,8,Fanonymously on 0800 555 111. Always
OL,9,Fdial 999 in an emergency."
